{"tid":693412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"河南3歲男童餵剛滿月弟弟食螺絲釘 緊急送院","createTime":"2018-06-07T12:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:43:16.000Z","uid":22349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"76d8b40e5ace5125d2c79b70578e16e3653bbf18","tid":693412,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:32:54.000Z","msg":"河南一名3歲男童日前和剛出生37天的弟弟獨處，其母回家後發現弟弟哭鬧不止，還口吐白沫且嘴唇發紫，詢問哥哥後得悉他竟將3顆螺絲餵給弟弟，嚇得立即將弟弟送往醫院治療。<br />\n<br />\n據消化科主任李小芹表示，周二（5日）下午4時許，家長帶着兒子到院求診，稱上午已帶兒子到縣級醫院，檢查發現胃裏有3顆螺絲，但是因為嬰兒還小，醫院不敢冒此風險，建議她們轉院到省醫院治理。 <br />\n<br />\n李小芹續指，她當時立即安排男嬰進行檢查，發現釘子還在胃裏，還幸螺絲吞進肚子的過程中沒有劃傷食道，最終可透過穿胃鏡，將3枚3.5厘米的螺絲取出。"},{"pid":"ea2eba58dabdd6a761b6e53e8718c7737778f3a1","tid":693412,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陷害自己屋企人正仆街"},{"pid":"93a57685cd482f0b7ed66d96b5ebff1258dd5ae5","tid":693412,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:35:59.000Z","msg":"補充鐵質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b947e41ccde6ae3b9c54292bccac279979fd34be","tid":693412,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽！細佬食螺絲呀！"},{"pid":"96e0baf570ea7cc594b6f977d089e271d0994b0b","tid":693412,"uid":22902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"少咗細佬分家產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815d9a906c29655db7814060f3d128d77233b764","tid":693412,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"真。螺絲粉😆"},{"pid":"8c35fbd190417206ad2796583a366cc9557d3d2a","tid":693412,"uid":162073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea2eba58dabdd6a761b6e53e8718c7737778f3a1","tid":693412,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"